### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### Create a Test Task
POST http://localhost:3001/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First MongoDB Task",
  "description": "Testing MongoDB Atlas connection",
  "priority": "high",
  "status": "todo",
  "userId": "1",
  "tags": ["test", "mongodb"]
}

### Get All Tasks
GET http://localhost:3001/api/tasks?userId=1

### Get Tasks by Status
GET http://localhost:3001/api/tasks?userId=1&status=todo

### Get Dashboard Stats
GET http://localhost:3001/api/stats/dashboard?userId=1

### Create a Project
POST http://localhost:3001/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Personal Projects",
  "description": "My personal todo items",
  "color": "#6a5af9",
  "userId": "1"
}

### Get All Projects
GET http://localhost:3001/api/projects?userId=1
